Package: ORSRouting
Type: Package
Title: Batch routing distance computations using OpenRouteService
Version: 0.9.0
Date: 2022-08-23
Authors@R: person("Lieth", "Jonas", email = "jonas.lieth@gesis.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jonas Lieth <jonas.lieth@gesis.org>
Description: Flexible interface to (custom) OpenRouteService instances.
    The package enables qualitative and quantitative route computations,
    accessibility analyses and distance matrix calculations using route
    distances (i.e., routing through real streets). It is primarily aimed at
    processing moderately large datasets and thus supports the setup and usage
    of custom OpenRouteService instances. However, it is also possible to use
    the public API given a valid key.
